full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/18/2023 Form 1 - 181a (Rev. 4-1-77)Y UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE IMMIGRATION AND INATURALIZATION SERVICE REFER TO THIS FILE NO. A21 198 924 Date: PHAM, Thao Van 1805 West Adams street SANTA ANA, CALIFORNIA. 92704 Your application for status as a permanent resident has been received. When proc- essing has been completed, you will be invited to appear for medical examination and interview. To avoid delay in the processing of your application, please do not telephone or write while your case is pending. However, if there is a change in your address, employ- ment or marital status, please notify this office promptly by mail referring to the above file number. Sincerely yours, District Director (Page 3)
